  <summary date="2021-09-17T15:11:56Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Lawful Access to Encrypted Data Act

This bill requires certain technology companies to ensure that they can decode encrypted information on their services and products in order to provide such information to law enforcement. It also establishes requirements and procedures for assisting law enforcement agencies in accessing encrypted data.</summary>
